UPDATE places SET description = 'Nigeria is all energy, from Afrobeats and fashion to food, markets, art, and unforgettable city life. Travelers who enjoy creativity, momentum, and strong cultural presence will find it one of West Africa''s most dynamic experiences. Afrobeats, creative energy, beach escapes, royal heritage, and big-city dynamism make Nigeria vibrant, bold, and culturally unforgettable.' WHERE type = 'country' AND name = 'Nigeria';
UPDATE places SET description = 'North Korea interests a very specific kind of traveler, one drawn to monumental architecture, choreographed spectacle, and rare access to an unusually closed society. The appeal is less conventional tourism than singular perspective. Monumental architecture, choreographed public spaces, and extreme rarity make it one of the world''s most unusual travel experiences.' WHERE type = 'country' AND name = 'North Korea';
UPDATE places SET description = 'North Macedonia offers travelers lakeside beauty in Ohrid, Ottoman-era streets, mountain scenery, and hearty Balkan hospitality. It is scenic, approachable, and especially rewarding for those who like slow, affordable cultural travel. Lakeside views, Ottoman-era neighborhoods, mountain monasteries, and hearty hospitality give it an easy, rewarding Balkan appeal.' WHERE type = 'country' AND name = 'North Macedonia';
UPDATE places SET description = 'Norway gives travelers dramatic fjords, scenic rail lines, fishing villages, modern design, and a sense of clean, spacious calm. It is hard to beat for travelers who want nature with comfort and precision. Fjords, rail journeys, Arctic light, cozy waterfront cities, and outdoor freedom make Norway feel calm, dramatic, and deeply restorative.' WHERE type = 'country' AND name = 'Norway';